Class WindowChangeProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mhs.compsys.processors.WindowChangeProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IChangeProcessor

    public class WindowChangeProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IChangeProcessor
    This Processor will recognize changes in the windows and quantify those. It will return WINDOW_APPLICATION_AREA_UPDATE, WINDOW_TITLE_BAR_CLICK, and WINDOW_TITLE_CHANGE
